:INFO
AI Tools for Novelists
A curated list of AI writing tools suited for long-form fiction work. Each tool has different strengths depending on your workflow stage.

:TASK
[ ] Sudowrite: best for scene generation and prose rewriting
[ ] ChatGPT: strong for brainstorming and outline structure
[ ] Claude: excellent for editing passes and consistency checks
[ ] Novelcrafter: project management plus AI integration
[ ] Scrivener + AI plugin: for writers already in the Scrivener ecosystem

:NOTE
No single tool does everything well. Many novelists use one tool for drafting and a different one for editing. Test a few and settle on a two-tool stack.

